{"id": 603, "genre": 1001, "title": "你什么时候会觉得自己活得“糙”？", "description": "用……洗衣皂洗了头的时候……", "record_count": 11032, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201606071944367YC8MS02tNJRKnlA.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-11-04T10:53:16Z", "options": [{"id": 22272, "content": "发现别人洗脸都要用洗面奶的时候 我通常用水泼...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285562}, {"id": 23040, "content": "家里乱的下不去脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 290238}, {"id": 22273, "content": "用牙膏洗了脸的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 228155}, {"id": 22018, "content": "为什么要用护发素", "image": null, "praise_count": 475, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 263797}, {"id": 22274, "content": "出门前对着镜子看到自己没刮胡子的样子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 42858}, {"id": 22019, "content": "一块香皂解决所有清洁问题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 119, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1688}, {"id": 22275, "content": "明明值得庆祝的日子，却一个人窝在宿舍吃泡面", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267069}, {"id": 26627, "content": "又不是处女座 糙不糙点怎么了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313639}, {"id": 22020, "content": "不出门脸都懒得洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1028, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 225731}, {"id": 22276, "content": "患懒癌，偶尔不卸妆就睡觉的处女座", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285575}, {"id": 22021, "content": "困了就在泡沫板上盖上报纸睡觉的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 248355}, {"id": 22022, "content": "已经快30岁了，依然穿的和学生一样。", "image": null, "praise_count": 619, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 269131}, {"id": 22278, "content": "明明打算不加班，却发现非加不可的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106997}, {"id": 22023, "content": "做一次饭能吃一个星期", "image": null, "praise_count": 75, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 276118}, {"id": 22279, "content": "一个星期都不用洗面奶洗脸的时候，不但周末不会洗头的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285583}, {"id": 22535, "content": "周末放假懒得刮胡子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283570}, {"id": 23047, "content": "天天对着不需要化妆的人…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289636}, {"id": 22024, "content": "玩游戏太晚了就直接睡了洗漱什么的就下次了", "image": null, "praise_count": 732, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238355}, {"id": 22280, "content": "头发好几天不洗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285537}, {"id": 22025, "content": "每天早上不得不去外面吃早餐的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 187946}, {"id": 22026, "content": "自从看到隔壁寝室的妹子吃个水果摆盘之后", "image": null, "praise_count": 72, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 236889}, {"id": 22027, "content": "世界那么大，和我没啥关系~", "image": null, "praise_count": 433, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212722}, {"id": 22283, "content": "没洗澡只是洗脸刷牙洗脚就爬床睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285616}, {"id": 22028, "content": "这玩意基本是拖延症的结果之一", "image": null, "praise_count": 266, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375}, {"id": 22029, "content": "一想到还有一大盆衣服要洗的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 364, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169547}, {"id": 22541, "content": "被子就不叠了吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273164}, {"id": 22030, "content": "和美女聊天时永远不知道她们说的护肤品和衣服的牌子", "image": null, "praise_count": 171, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279206}, {"id": 22031, "content": "袜子喜欢攒起来一起洗……", "image": null, "praise_count": 786, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 237122}, {"id": 22032, "content": "洗澡只用洗发露就能从头洗到脚", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 173474}, {"id": 22288, "content": "公司食堂的饭吃的干干净净", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285642}, {"id": 22544, "content": "养成了熬夜的习惯后…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287160}, {"id": 22033, "content": "想去见某个人的时候连件像样的外套都没有，只好向室友借", "image": null, "praise_count": 121, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283770}, {"id": 22289, "content": "别人把钱花在化妆品上，自己把钱花在吃上...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 261037}, {"id": 23057, "content": "起床匆匆，用冷水擦一下眼睛就算洗脸了。然后就什么也不涂就上课去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289727}, {"id": 22034, "content": "从一堆穿过的袜子里面，挑不出还能穿的了", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 270740}, {"id": 22290, "content": "屋里好多东西都得着好久", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 238704}, {"id": 22035, "content": "是真糙..", "image": null, "praise_count": 139, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 232073}, {"id": 22291, "content": "囤了一堆化妆品永远懒得用", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 285698}, {"id": 22036, "content": "4天不洗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 353, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 160111}, {"id": 22292, "content": "喝挂不卸妆倒床睡第二天起来后", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 249162}, {"id": 28692, "content": "不想买衣服了，因为懒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 326253}, {"id": 22037, "content": "上厕所，翻纸篓", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 281660}, {"id": 22293, "content": "每当吃饭只能想起麦当劳和泡面的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105873}, {"id": 22549, "content": "照镜子的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 274922}, {"id": 23317, "content": "基本上一个月会有一次放肆 玩到很晚啥也不洗直接去睡 第二天油腻的头发暗黄的脸?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 291740}, {"id": 24085, "content": "一个女生扛起一桶水换在饮水机上，一气呵成，脸不红气不喘。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 296562}, {"id": 25877, "content": "双人床一半是杂物一半是睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 304447}, {"id": 22038, "content": "熨斗会把衣服烫个大洞吧？", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 22039, "content": "肚子饿了自己不会弄吃的", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 216032}, {"id": 22551, "content": "牙膏不分早晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 287179}]}